<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM4.7.7">
<l>kōlāl niraimēyt taveṅkō valarkōvē</l>
<l>nālā kiyavē tiyarmaṉ ṉiyanāṅkūr</l>
<l>cēlār vayalcūḻ tiruveḷ ḷakkuḷattuḷ</l>
<l>mālē yeṉaval viṉaitīrt taruḷāyē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Our king of the cowherders who grazed the herd with a staff,</l>
<l>Māl in Tiruveḷḷakkuḷam girded by carp-filled paddy fields</l>
<l>In Nāṅkūr where dwell experts of the four Vedas,</l>
<l>Be gracious, removing my harsh karma!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
